The Station Details screen has two different layouts depending on its state.
The first layout will display when there are no alerts posted. 
In this layout, the user can post an alert for the chosen station by typing in the text box and clicking the “Post” button.
The second layout will display if there has already been an alert posted.
In this layout, users can view the alert information for the chosen station. 
To edit an alert post, the publisher of the alert must click the “EDIT” button
To delete an alert post, the publisher of the alert must click the “DELETE” button
There is a news feed for the alert post in which additional details may be displayed to the user. 
Users can choose to post in the feed by entering information in the text box and clicking the “POST FEED” button.
